main event: A civilian reported seeing a bright light in the sky over Greenebay, Wisconsin, on 19 Sep 61.
interesting points: The light was reported to be changing colors and moving erratically.,The sighting lasted approximately 10-15 minutes.,The observation was reported to the Greenebay Air Force Base., The report included both ground radar and visual observations., A request for review regarding the radar sighting was initiated by the US Air Force.
sighted object: a bright light in the sky
